editorialDecl.normalization:
Latin spellings, punctuation and capitalization normalized;
                    "e" endings changed "ae"; "u" changed to "v"; "c" changed to "t"; "j" changed to
                    "i"; abbreviations of numbers are expanded and marked by the expan element; all other
                    abbreviations are expanded and not marked;spelling normalizations are given as a choice between sic (as in the
                    source) and corr (the corrected version);
